title: HOUR 1 - Warriors, Eagles, Broncos
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Warriors, Eagles, Broncos
description:
Colin discusses a potential suspension for Draymond Green after fighting with a teammate and why this is a good thing for the Warriors

The Eagles are having a great season but they're a year or two away from contending for a title

The Broncos must win tonight against the Colts

 

Guest: Albert Breer
